  "texts": [
    "To bridge this gap, the paper proposes a comprehensive integration of soft and hard laws.",
    "Soft laws should be explicitly updated to emphasize affordability, literacy, and international cooperation, providing ethical guidance and public pressure to complement hard laws.",
    "Concurrently, hard laws should adopt market-friendly but socially responsible regulationssuch as guided pricing mechanisms, public service assurances through institutions like libraries, and legislative frameworks mandating",
    "TorontoDeclaration (n.d.).",
    "Inclusive AI must be shaped by a diverse range of voices in all areas from strategy development, data gathering, algorithmic design, implementation, and user impact, with the goal of respecting the right to live free from discrimination."
  ]
